{CoreyMcCormack}
Hey, my name is Corey and I’m fourteen years old. I need your help, Joey!
[[...|next1]]

{CoreyMcCormack}
Last year my family took a trip to Coney Island. That’s my mom, my step-dad, me and my twin brother Carey. It was awesome!
[[...|next2]]

{CoreyMcCormack}
But the problem is, ever since we got back, Carey has been acting weird.

[[...|next3]]

{CoreyMcCormack}
He doesn’t wanna play baseball anymore, he just wants to sit in an armchair and read the sports pages. He yells at the TV and keeps a stash of beers under his bed!

[[...|next4]]

{CoreyMcCormack}
I’m here today to find out once and for all: what happened to you Carey?

[[Continue|endScene]]
